     "board": "Planning Board",
     "event_type": "variance_special_permit",
     "stage": "approved",
     "summary": "The Planning Board unanimously approved a Site Plan Special Permit for demolition of the existing structure at 69 Puritan Road and construction of a new approximately 3,000-square-foot single-family residence with attached garage and in-ground pool in the A-3 Zoning District. The project carries prior approvals from the Conservation and Historical Commissions and is designed to comply with floodplain requirements by elevating the structure above base flood elevation. The Board noted concerns about the extent of paved surfaces and dual curb cuts in the front yard and recommended reducing impervious coverage and enhancing landscaping.",
